chisma und das Streben nach Kirchenreform prägten nicht nur seine Zeit, sondern auch Mulbergs Vita.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 0aBeguineszSwitzerlandzBaselxHistory. 4aBasel. 4aBeginen. 4aDominikaner. 4aMulberg, Johannes. 4aOrdensreform. 7aHISTORY / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA History 2000 - 2014z9783110635836oZDB-23-GHI0 cprintz978305003543740uhttps://doi.org/10.1524/978305004736240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783050047362423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783050047362/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GHIc2000d2014